Small summary of the story:

First, the terrorists attacked an office that is located in Western Europe , CTs tried to stop but the terrorists escaped.
On the way back home, the terrorists got stuck in the snowy mountains of Austria. The CT's captured the terrorists and brought them to Sweden for a trial. Somehow, the terrorists once again managed to escape and hide themselves in a local store in Sweden, with the name Ica Maxi.
After the CTs had a laggy atmosphere, the terrorists used this advantage, stole a helicopter and returned back to their base, in the Middle East. Lets see how the story continues...

Here comes my latest map (maybe last for a long time), hosties_base_of_terror. The map has a dusty theme and is located at the secret base of the terrorists somewhere in the desert. Some smart CT's picked up a track of odd chocolate shaped footsteps that led all the way from hosties_planet_cookie to the hidden town in the desert. The town looks normal, no signs of any terrorist who might be hiding somewhere. It is CTs task to locate and punish the terrorists who are s planning another bomb attempt somewhere in the world.

Took me a few days to make this map, although some problems occured which stopped me from releasing it. The strange 'bouncy physics' thing happened so I removed some street cardboard bombs I had planted out in the map, so it would fit the theme better. Thought that it might be the problem so I removed them, but don't worry, there are more fun stuff to do...

PIC1. The map
PIC2. The secret terrorist base
PIC3. Entering the T base
PIC4. The map
PIC5. *SECRET* Unlockable, wieldable cardboard suicidebombs that make you go BOOM! when you press !USE (E)!
PIC6. Terrorist who is still flying after he blew himself up in the air.

There are 2 ways to escape the base. First, there's the normal rebel way, leading up to a house on a hill where you can choose to rebel from the window or jump out and deliver yourself. 2, the V.I.P escape, only available for 2 terrorists. The V.I.P escape will teleport you to another house. The T's have already planted a secret dynamite-balloon which will fly over to the backside of the simon says wall and explode itself, damaging the CTs. You can also choose to open the door to go outside or take the way out by going up on the roof.

There are 2 jails with 4 rooms. You must climb up on the jails if you play S4S. There is another optional house to climb up on and play S4S.

*SECRET* Wieldable suicide packages, are unlocked by a secret combination. I have added 2 packs and those will be available every round, but you know that I only tell the secret to the people that deserve it :d
By pressing E, it will take your life, send you up in the air and probably a few CTs to. But be careful, the bomb also hits your fellow T comrades!
You can easily see which terrorist has a bomb planted on his back by looking for a cardboard package that is placed on the back! CTs, watchout!

*Forgot to mention that there are 2 ways to escape from the jail too, 1 you can break the rusty metal bar window at 1 jail, 2, you can break the a wall which leads you to the old dried sewer passage. You would eventually end up crawling up from the well. Also, all lights are toggable, which means that you can either shoot or press USE! to switch the light off/on. Good when rebelling or escaping from jails!
*Lights in the T base do not work to switch off*

Things included in the map:
- 16 T spawn
- 16 CT spawn
- Buyzones for both teams
- 4 Cells including the Safe
- 2 Buildings wich you can enter
- 4 Cars with alarms
- A trailer with music
- 2 Secrets
- 3D Skybox
- Custom Skybox
- 2 Health regenerators, max 4 hp per second.

Please give comments about this map :)

Greetz Roy

IS_VOID by Target Practice

- This map is an ICE SKATE (is_) fight map.
- is_void is the third ice skate map released since the birth of this gametype.
- This map is the first to bring the diversity of multiple weapons incorporating knife and sniper combat.
- AFKers will be killed after 20 seconds each round.
- No known bugs.
- 5 hours build-time.

_________________________________________________

PLEASE NOTE: SET sv_airaccelerate to 300 for best results!

_________________________________________________

THE GAMETYPE

ICE SKATE (is_) is a custom gametype introduced by HellRaisedSurfer. 

This gametype involves skating across a surface and killing the opposing team.
This is done by using a combination of strafing (A and D keys) and mouse movement to gain momentum.

_________________________________________________

- Special thanks go to Icecreamlock for custom textures.
- Thanks to Karatekaefer for the skybox.
- Thanks to the MapJunkies server provided by Icecreamlock.
- Thanks to all the testers who played the exclusive release.

_________________________________________________

WWW.MAPJUNKIES.COM

_________________________________________________

INSTALLATION:

- To install the map you will need to copy&paste (or extract the contents of the .rar if you wish) the .BSP file (is_void.bsp) into the 'maps' folder.
- To get to this folder you will need to go into:

- Program Files>Steam>Steamapps>counter-strike source>cstrike>maps.

- The .bsp file included in the download should go in your maps folder.

- Load up the game and you should be able to play it.

Is_teleport ------------------------------------------------ Map by Apexi Skybox by Karatekafer Custom textures by Icecreamlock ------------------------------------------------ Setting:It was a regular ice skating map until one kid had an idea. That idea was to change the game-play and open a new door in ice skate mapping. Teleports and Multi-levels. Before without teleports ice skating was a plain game-play. It limited where players could go and what they could do. Once this one kid developed the teleports and multilevel skating, the game-play was changed forever. ------------------------------------------------ Game-play: What happens is each team spawns on opposite sides of the map with a knife. The player walks off the spawn and starts strafing around. He/she can go through teleports to get to different parts of the map while still maintaining speed. He/she can go to the upper level to pick up a scout to shoot other players. Also there is one usp pistol that has a laser following it so the person with the pistol is easy to spot. What someone can also do is go down to the bottom platform and gain speed by going on the speed boosts multiple times. But watch out, if you don't turn enough you will fall off the edge and there is no turning back. ------------------------------------------------ Server Settings It is strongly suggested that the server admin puts sv_airaccelerate at 300. Any more or less will effect the game-play. ------------------------------------------------ Installation:Extract is_teleport.bsp into your cstrike>maps folder ------------------------------------------------ Other: This map was made entirely by Apexi from Mapjunkies.com Nothing was used without proper credits. A special thanks goes out to Karatekafer for the skybox, Icecreamlock for the glass texture, and all of the people who tested the map and made suggestions. I hope you enjoy the map and for more ice skating maps and other types of maps visit mapjunkies.com.
